---
---
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 overflow-hidden hero-section">
  <div class="container-custom relative z-10">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="slide-up" transition:animate="slide">
        <h1 class="mb-6 text-secondary-900 dark:text-white leading-tight">
          Let <span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Parker</span> handle the busy work.<br>
        </h1>
       <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-white dark:text-white">
        We take care of the websites.<br>
        So you can focus on the jobsites.
        </p><br>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-white dark:text-white">
        What's your time worth?
        </p>

        <br>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
            Contact us
          </a>
          <a href="https://blog.parkerautomation.io" target="_blank" class="btn-outline flex items-center">
            Blog
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/parkerautomation/parker-site" target="_blank" class="btn-outline flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="https://www.reshot.com/preview-assets/icons/KWSM4GTXY6/human-robot-KWSM4GTXY6.svg">
